    "description": "Discipline: Waijia\nSkill: Arm Strike\nType: Normal\nQi: 2\n\nYou spin on the ball of your foot, whipping your fists at everyone around you. Make an Arm Strike Skill roll against all opponents around you (each target must be within five feet of your body). This allows you to strike each of them with enough force to do normal Damage and to push them back in a straight line, 5 feet per Rank of Waijia. Cathartic: You hit with enough force that each of your opponents slam into anyone in their path when they are pushed back, and do 1d10 Damage per Qi Rank you possess to those they strike.",
